params.name: data

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the Product for which to list SKUs. The parent takes the format: products/{product_id}. Supports products/- to retrieve SKUs for all products.

params.name: data.account
params.description: Required. Resource name of the reseller. Format: accounts/{account_id}.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. Requested page size. Server might return fewer results than requested. If unspecified, at most 100 SKUs will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A token identifying a page of results, if other than the first one. Optional.

params.name: data.language_code
params.description: Optional. The BCP-47 language code, such as "en-US". If specified, the response will be localized to the corresponding language code. Default is "en-US".
